flowRoot.flowPara: This Battleship has just moved into the second orbital of Corporate Base 3322. It has 3 delta-vee remaining. It spends 2 delta-vee to bombard Corporate Base 3322.

The Battleship has 2 base bombardment power. It loses 1 bombardment power because there is 1 orbital between it and the asset; giving a total bombardment power of 1. It receives 2 chances to bombard the asset because it spent 2 delta-vee on the maneuver.
Corporate Base 3322 has a bombardment resistance of 3.
In this case it rolled 1 hit, and does 1 damage to Corporate Base 3322.
The Battleship rolls a six-sided dice for each delta-vee it spent on the maneuver. For each roll that is higher than the bombardment resistance it does damage equal to its total bombardment power.
